CNCP v1 23509
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#11724: Adds the `key: number` property to a slot props if this slot has `v-if`",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:22:19.477761+00:00",
  "text": "Adds the `key: number` property to a slot props if this slot has `v-if`\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.4.38\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nSpecify a slot props without the `key` property. Add `v-if` for this slot or the parent `<template />`.\n\n### What is expected?\n\nThe `key` property is missing if not physically specified.\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nThe `key: number` property is added.\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: slots",
    "🔩 p2-edge-case"
  ],
